	program + command + option + argument
	program + n*argument
	program + optional argument
	â€¦

Options:
->SYSTEM
    -h --help   
    -clr {True, False}, --clear_terminal {True, False} 
    -p PATH, --path PATH    
->TEXT
    -t TITLE, --title TITLE    
    -xl XLABEL, --xlabel XLABEL    
    -yl YLABEL, --ylabel YLABEL    
->LOOK
    -c COLOR, --color COLOR     
    -m MARKER, --marker MARKER      
->STATUS
    -s SLEEP, --sleep SLEEP


